    },
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "logs:CreateLogGroup",
        "logs:CreateLogStream",
        "logs:PutLogEvents"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:logs:*:*:*"
    }
  ]
}
```

As you can see the policy then only has the `PutItem` not the `GetItem` permission sio the /find call will fail with an unauthorized error. Right now as a workaround I'm creating a dummy function that will never execute by starting with `if False:` and putting all the required actions in there but its ugly

